### Backend: Get yield curve (uses FRED data)
@backendUrl = http://localhost:8000
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/yields?date=2025-02-05
Accept: application/json

### FRED API: 1-Month Treasury
GET {{url}}?series_id=DGS1MO&api_key={{key}}&file_type=json&observation_start=2025-02-05&observation_end=2025-02-05
Accept: application/json